        <mxCell id="G4kx3IIp9so120Mb9tM5-65" parent="G4kx3IIp9so120Mb9tM5-76" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;container=0;" value="&lt;div align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;3. In order to pin exact dependency, we have to do dependency resolution of dependency graph:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;- Step 1. Parse already specified direct dependencies in requirements.txt/pyproject.toml file.&lt;br&gt;- Step 2. Find all dependencies of direct dependencies (transitive dependencies from direct dependencies).&lt;br&gt;- Step 3. Continue Step 2. in recursive way if there is no errors and dependency conflicts/hell (e.g., circular dependency).&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
